  "lastUpdatedAt": "2023-11-30T14:43:56.1560717+00:00",
  "longDescription": "Imagine a world where internal communication flows smoothly, and efficiently, where all members of your team receive information seamlessly in one place.\n \nExperience the end-to-end internal messaging experience with BeComm. A solution developed within Microsoft Teams that allows you to administer and manage internal communications with people in your organization in a simple and agile way.\n \nYou'll enjoy an intuitive interface, instant and dynamic notifications, the ability to analyze the effectiveness of every communication sent, and much more.\n \nCollect all the information to analyze, manage and optimize your communication!\n \nDownload our app today in Microsoft Teams, and take your team collaboration to the next level, either on Microsoft Teams, Outlook or Microsoft 365.\n\n**Note: This application requires that end users, the one receiving messages, have the receiving bot installed. You can find this bot in the FAQ section to download and as an IT Admin use any deployment tool to install that bot for end users. If you are not an IT Admin, please contact an organization IT Admin for assistance.**\n\n**To get started with the application, please refer to the FAQ within the app, so you can enjoy BeComm.**\n\n**Is BeComm functionality limited in the trial period?**\nNo, trial version is fully functional.\n\n**What happens after the trial period?**\n\nOnce the 30-day trial period is over (counted from the installation date), to continue enjoying the benefits of BeComm, you will need to subscribe to one of our subscription plans. The subscription will allow you to continue using BeComm.\nFor more information, please, fill out [this form](https://forms.office.com/r/jn65Dhadxn)\n\n**Need assistance or support during the trial period or after you sign up?**\n\nOur support team is always available to answer your questions, provide technical assistance and help you with anything you need. You can access our support section via the following link:\n\n[Support Link](https://servicedesk.newtech.com.ar)",
